{"tid":735107,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中超＞西甲！保連奴是主動選擇恒大 指中超前景好","createTime":"2018-07-09T08:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T00:58:44.000Z","uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78aab975fd025844cd040896be6e06235c30068d","tid":735107,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"　　香港時間今天淩晨，廣州恒大官方宣佈，巴塞球員保連奴租借加盟，租借期為一年，在恒大的官方公告中，表示保連奴是主動選擇回中超的。<br />\n<br />\n　　廣州恒大在官方公告中寫道：「保連奴表示，中超聯賽水平逐年提高，發展前景很好。經過在恒大、巴塞的鍛鍊，同時跟隨巴西國家隊在世界盃又得到了很好的曆練，這次主動選擇重新返回中超聯賽，希望能給廣州隊和廣州球迷帶來更多冠軍，也希望給中超聯賽帶來更多精彩。」　　<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　保連奴今年30歲，2017年夏天以4000萬歐元的轉會費加盟巴塞，他為巴塞出戰49場，攻進9球貢獻2次助攻。今年的世界盃，保連奴也是巴西隊絕對主力，出戰5場353分鐘，攻進1球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/07/09/1/1b26c92f3585a2ddbf4fd3f97aaac918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F1%2F1b26c92f3585a2ddbf4fd3f97aaac918.jpg&h=372f2ef1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810363049b65e9d0cc49476f02e8cc47b8a6f028","tid":735107,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"高人工<br />\n福利好<br />\n無人敢屌佢<br />\n無壓力<br />\n鳩鳩流流又一場<br />\nDream Job"},{"pid":"f0bbb11d27de175321b1510696c09a4cd23f3e3a","tid":735107,"uid":155197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"想叫雞炸"},{"pid":"fdbf100f1fd1dbcbe2c237c2657bf00c8cdfa07f","tid":735107,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"度假一年再戰西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31db458c30ef3a7cc0d0942f285a4b596d0dbb85","tid":735107,"uid":18674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"當疤condom咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be625b3deb0a4e29b5be89b58bf7a389b3e29aad","tid":